.\n  - User could control using water temperature.\n Standard accessory. \n  - Magnetic stirrer for stirring 6 bottles at one time.'),(9,'Magnetic stirrer','Dyeing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/001_04_02.jpg','Low & high speed mising of 6 dye bottle in stable speed\n  with DC brushless motor. Semi-permanent stainless steel\n  plate and convenient operation by compact design'),(10,'Lab. IR (Infrared Rays) Dyeing Machine','Dyeing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/001_05.jpg','Wireless sensor guarantee no maintenance of temperature sensor.\n  (Patents, design register)\n The dyeing pots are rotated 360 degrees and guarantee even dyeing.\n   - CPU Micro processor DLS-8800.\n Be fit for various kinds of textile dyeing. (Knit & Woven, Yarn)\n  - Spandex(Poly, N/Tactel, Acetate), P/Matte Jersey, Polar Fleece. \n  - Blended Fabric, Micro Fiber, P/N, P/W, A/N, P/A.\n Save time due to next dyeing reservation.\n Pleasant circumstance in laboratory due to no gas, very silent safety & \n   economic working compare to the PEG machine.\n Because the dyeing pot is made by press and special electronic\n  processing instead of trimming it is prevented from contamination and\n  very fit P/C, P/R, P/W, P/N due to various pot capacity such as 150 milli-liter,\n  300 milli-liter,500 milli-liter, 1000 milli-liter, 2000 milli-liter, 4000 milli-liter.\n Dosing system for reactive dyeing. (Option).\n Large graphic display for dyeing status on LCD monitor.\n Easy installation due to air cooling system.\n Durable 32bit micro processor CPU. (Accuracy ±0.5?)\n Various language. (English, Chinese, German, Korean)'),(11,'Lab. IR (Infrared Rays) Auto Dosing Dyeing Machine','Dyeing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/001_06.jpg','Automatically auxiliary chemicals (Soda, Alkali) dose during sample\n   dyeing and repeatability improvement between Lab and production\n  facilities. \n One-stop dyeing for blend fabrics (P/C, P/R) and holder to be\n   compatible with normal pot. \n The dyeing pots are rotated 360 Degrees and guarantee even dyeing.\n  - CPU Micro processor DLS-8800. \n Be fit for various kinds of textile dyeing. (Knit & Woven, Yarn)\n  - Spandex(Poly, N/Tactel, Acetate), P/Matte Jersey, Polar Fleece. \n  - Blended Fabric, Micro Fiber, P/N, P/W, A/N, P/A.\n Save time due to next dyeing reservation.\n Pleasant circumstance in laboratory due to no gas, very silent safety\n  & economic working compare to the PEG machine. \n Because the dyeing pot is made by press and special electronic\n  processing instead of trimming it is prevented from contamination\n  and very fit P/C, P/R, P/W, P/N due to various pot capacity such\n  as 150 milli-liter, 300 milli-liter, 500 milli-liter. \n Dosing system for reactive dyeing.\n Large graphic display for dyeing status on LCD monitor.\n Easy installation due to air cooling system.\n Durable 32bit micro processor CPU. (Accuracy ±0.5?)\n Various language. (English, Chinese, German, Korean)'),(12,'Mini Sample Dyeing Machine','Dyeing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/001_07.jpg','It\' s can be dyeing for buyer\' s wants.\n CPU Micro processor controller.\n CPU - Fully digitalized functions.\n Alarm - Easy to check and see machine troubles.\n The fabric transport of dyeing machine to easy control\n   by program.\n Reserve and end functions - Excellent working efficiency.\n It\' s compare presently temperature with setting\n  temperature.\n Easy to operate.\n Working with liquid. (Standard)\n Working with dyeing drum. (Option)\n Testing capacity ? 1.8~12yard. (Based on 250gram/yard)\n Testing capacity ? 2.0~20yard. (Based on 300gram/yard)'),(13,'Water Bath Shaker','Dyeing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/001_08.jpg','Easy to operate UniController incorporating temperature control\n  and shaking control. (Suitable for 16 X 1 bath only) \n Ensures precise testing with a pre-settable digital timer.\n Soft start and braking by inverter not to overload driving motor. \n Noiseless driving axle.\n Equipped with door shock absorber for operator convenience.\n Corrosion resistance bath plate, flask holder and excellent durability.\n Removable flask holder plate and easy cleaning.\n Soaping available.\n Wool, A/W dyeing.\n Selectable various baths.\n  - 16 X 1 bath, 24 X 1 bath, 30 X 1 bath, 16 X 2 bath, 30 X 2 bath,\n    50 X 2 bath. '),(14,'Auto Coating Machine','Finishing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/003_01.jpg','Accuracy temperature control by PID auto-tuning function.\n Quick dry and equalized temperature distribution by \n   forced convection up & down air flow system. \n Repeatability improvement by sensor system for knife\n   zero-setting.\n Coating knife is consist of doctor knife(0.5mm-Standard,\n    1.0mm, 2.0mm-Option) & Comma knife. \n Another type & thickness of knife is customized.\n The exhaust fan on the roof ventilate to outside the gas of\n    chamber inside. \n Convenient operation with automatic driving mechanism.\n Consistent coating speed and ensures standardized\n   quality.\n Precise coating of 0.01mm thickness on one side\n   of material.\n Adjustable knife inclination, coating, thickness, speed\n   and distance.'),(15,'Manual Coating Machine','Finishing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/003_02.jpg','Cost-effective coating tester.\n Coating knife is consist of Doctor knife(0.5mm-standard,\n    1.0mm & 2.0mm-Option) & Comma knife.Another type & \n   thickness of knife is customized. \n Precise coating of 0.01mm thickness on one side\n   of material.\n Adjustable knife inclination, coating thickness.\n Easy operation in small space.'),(16,'Spray / Knife & Gravure Coating Machine','Finishing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/003_03.jpg','Spray & knife coater is switchable. The variety working processing.\n Equal spray coating by precise mist type nozzle.\n Glass bottle 2 liter and magnetic stirring - Prevent solidify & \n   precipitation. \n After spray coating, the extra cleaning 2 liter glass bottle which fill \n   water or cleaning agent. \n Coater header is adjustable height, thickness, angle of knife.\n   There are nine(9) angle adjustable. \n Coating knife is consist of Doctor knife(0.5mm-Standard, 1.0mm,\n    2.0mm-Option) & Comma knife.\n   Another type & thickness of knife is customized. \n Anti scattering cover protects the spray to outside. \n Automatic transport a frame by high efficient inverter. \n  Which drives standard speed test.'),(17,'Screen Printing Machine','Finishing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/003_04.jpg','Semi-automatic screen printing.\n Adjustable squeegee inclination.\n Washable water-proof leather table.\n Accurate digital thickness gauge 0.01mm resolution.\n Adjustable printing speed and distance.\n Selectable printing with rubber squeegee or\n  electromagnetic bar.'),(18,'Lab. Dryer','Finishing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/003_05.jpg','Accuracy temperature control by PID auto-tuning function.\n Quick dry and equalized temperature distribution by\n  forced convection air flow system. \n Simultaneous use with coating testing machine.\n  (Coater-Option)\n Ergonomic shape & compact design.\n Pre-check the sample formation & color difference due to\n  production processing chemical such as composure. \n The exhaust fan on the roof ventilate to outside the gas\n  of chamber inside. \n Automatic sample delivery out with frame upon complete\n  the testing time.\n Actuator behind of top cover help prompt cooling for\n  next job.\n Sample damage by over heating can be protected by\n  over temperature limit function.'),(19,'Lab. Continuous Stenter','Finishing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/003_06.jpg','Accuracy temperature control by PID auto-tuning function.\n Forced convection air flow system equalize temperature \n   distribution in the chamber. \n Narrow inlet & outlet design prevent form temperature\n   vibration.\n Sample wide tension can be adjusted continuously.\n   It maximize the sample testing. \n The exhaust fan on the roof ventilate to outside the gas\n  from chamber. \n Upper & lower two nozzle design can be differ according\n  to air volume & air velocity which is for the best quality\n  of dry/setting. \n Suitable for various fabric such as Poly, Cotton Knit,\n  Woven, Spandex, Nylon etc. \n Same air flow with production stenter result in good\n  repeatability.\n Suitable for non-woven leather thicker sample.'),(20,'Lab. Continuous Net Dryer','Finishing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/004_04.jpg','Fabric tumbling effect gives the minimum shrinkage and touch feeling.\n By know-how of continuous stenter, the upper & lower two nozzle air circulation system equalizes the temperature\n  distribution, same air velocity, air volume. which results equal drying. \n Accuracy temperature control by PID auto-tuning function.\n The continuous slot nozzle makes soft touch feeling and also can used for Non-woven, Pile Fabric, Brushed Fabric. \n Due to thickness(5mm~100mm) adjustment of mesh conveyor, the web status fiber can make non-woven form\n  by the high temperature. \n Multi step of exhaust fan on the roof keeps suitable amount of humidity inside chamber avoids yellowing of light\n  color fabric. \n For 2 chamber system can set different temperature in first & second chamber.\n Just end of exit equipped up & down cooling system.\n Same air flow with production net dryer result in good repeatability.'),(21,'Lab. Steamer','Finishing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/003_07.jpg','Accuracy temperature control by PID auto-tuning function.\n Quick dry and equalized temperature distribution by forced\n   convection up & down air flow system. (Dry mode) \n Steaming with saturated steam.\n Ergonomic shape & compact design.\n Adjustable temperature range for drying, curing and\n   setting from 20 Degrees-celsius to 250 Degrees-celsius. \n Moisture regulation of 20 to 100%.\n Electric steam generator inside machine, no separate\n  facility required.\n Automatic sample delivery out with frame upon complete\n  the testing time \n E-control test. (Option)\n Sample damage by overheating can be protected by over\n  temperature limit function.'),(22,'Gravure Coating Vertical Type Padder Machine','Finishing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/003_08.jpg','Trust cylinder guarantee the equal pressure left & center\n  & right it drives accurate pick up rate \n Variety working-One side coating processing(Gravure\n   coating) dyeing & finishing & impregnating of textile. \n High efficient inverter motor, speed controller, digital\n  tachometer control a precise rotating speed in low speed\n  & high speed. \n Front air regulator makes user be able to adjust air\n  pressure through precise pressure gauge. \n Ergonomic shape & compact design.\n Safety device-Two protector between roller and\n  emergency stop switch & bar. '),(23,'Horizontal & Vertical Type Padder Machine','Finishing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/003_09.jpg','Trust cylinder guarantee the equal pressure left & center\n   & right it drives accurate pick up rate. \n Variety working-Coating processing(Laminating) dyeing\n  & finishing & impregnating of textile. \n Universal working-Horizontal & vertical with same machine.\n High efficient inverter motor, speed controller, digital\n  tachometer control a precise rotating speed in low speed\n  & high speed. \n Front air regulator makes user be able to adjust air\n  pressure through precise pressure gauge. \n Table type-Ergonomic shape & compact design.\n Safety device-Two protector between roller and\n  emergency stop switch & bar.'),(24,'Horizontal Type Padder Machine','Finishing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/003_10.jpg','Trust cylinder guarantee the equal pressure left & center\n  & right it drives accurate pick up rate.\n Variety working-Dyeing & finishing & impregnating\n  of textile.\n High efficient inverter motor, speed controller,\n  digital tachometer control a precise rotating speed in\n  low speed & high speed.\n Front air regulator makes user be able to adjust\n  air pressure through precise pressure gauge.\n Ergonomic shape & compact design.\n Safety device-Two protector between roller\n  and emergency stop switch & bar.'),(25,'Vertical Type Padder Machine','Finishing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/003_11.jpg','Trust cylinder guarantee the equal pressure left & center\n  & right it drives accurate pick up rate.\n Variety working-Dyeing & finishing & impregnating\n  of textile.\n High efficient inverter motor, speed controller,\n  digital tachometer control a precise rotating speed in\n  low speed & high speed.\n Front air regulator makes user be able to adjust\n  air pressure through precise pressure gauge.\n Ergonomic shape & compact design.\n Safety device-Two protector between roller\n  and emergency stop switch & bar.'),(26,'Lab. Calender Machine','Finishing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home/images/product/004_03.jpg','Depend on the industry, roller is differ. Standard model is two(2) roll\n   type and three(3) roll type is also possible. \n This lab. calender is used for treating the surface of sample material.\n  Surface is shined under high pressure and heated steel roll.\n Accurate temperature is controlled by digital PID controller.\n High efficient invertor motor, speed controller, digital tachometer control\n  a precise rotating speed in low speed & high speed. \n Two precise hydraulic regulator & pressure gauge adjust left\n  & right roller.\n Sample material transport device in front of roller help convenient work.\n Protection cover in front of two roller is for safety protection bar between\n  two roller & emergency foot switch is for safety. \n Polyamide roller is most wide use for calender. (Textile, Paper)\n Unwinder equipment & winder. (Optional)'),(27,'Forced Convection Oven','Finishing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/003_12.jpg','Temperature up to 150 degrees-celsius.\n Accuracy temperature control by microprocessor based\n   PID controller. (Auto tuning function) \n Quick dry and equalized temperature distribution by\n  forced convection air circulation flow system. .\n Transparent glass to see inside sample.\n Air circulation system on door top & bottom is able for\n  user to use high temperature with safety. \n For user safety & sample good condition equipped over\n  heat protector & overload protective device. \n More bigger size of chamber is customized. (Option)'),(28,'Temperature & Humidity Chamber','Finishing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/003_13.jpg','Accurate temperature control by digital PID controller and\n   easy operation.\n Electronic humidity sensor is able to control stable\n   humidity. This sensor high speed of communication\n   reaction and ling life time. \n Reservation function to test and easy operation.\n Inside of material is all stainless steel and shelf height is\n   simply adjustable.\n Transparent glass to see inside sample.\n For user safety & sample good condition equipped over\n   heat protector & overload protective device.\n   The size of chamber is customized. (Option) \n Recorder. (Option)'),(29,'Reactor Station Synthesizer','Finishing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/003_14.jpg','Four bath have each own temperature and allow operator four\n  different test.\n Block for insulation and cooling : Tube shape block provide\n  separate bath condition by minimizing heat interference from the\n  other bath.\n Heating block is made of teflon or ceramic coating guarantee\n  anti corrosion.\n Water coil with water circulating system prevent evaporation of\n  chemical solution.\n Supply gas(N2) keeps the original environment.\n Magnetic stirrer mixes chemical solution continuously.\n Wide range of testing vessel from 250 milli-liter flask ~ 25 milli-liter tube.\n Testing block turns up to 180 Degrees-celsius - Save the space.\n Testing reaction & synthesizing from high temperature to\n  low (-20 Degrees-celsius)temperature.\n User friendly - Touch screen monitor.'),(30,'Dynamic E/Spinning Machine','Finishing','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/003_15.jpg','X. Y. Z robot control system.\n Multi nozzle up to 4ea, each nozzle can be\n  control independently - High productivity.\n Spinning amount, speed, time, distance can be\n  adjustable every nozzle.\n Differ from hot melting/wet dry type, using positive(+)\n  and negative(-)voltage produce web shape of micro\n  & nano fiber.\n Due to multi nozzle can produce blend nano fiber.\n Not only small sample but also pilot scale sample\n  since large roller.\n Can produce a medical, engineering fiber for recovery\n  of tissue of three dimension.\n Real-time check of the operating status by PC controller.\n  (10.4\' touch screen)'),(31,'Wash Color Fastness Tester','Fastness','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/002_01.jpg','PID type temperature controller and re-settable digital timer.\n Soft start and braking by inverter not to overload driving motor.\n Easy to replace pots on coil spring holder incorporating a push and twist feature. \n Model DL-2002M : Interchangeable pots. (550 milli-liter small size and 1200 milli-liter large size) \n Leak proof pots at high temperature with a suitable rubber gasket.\n Equipped with door shock absorber for operator convenience\n Auto-alarm after working finish.\n Convenient operation and cleaning.\n Standards : KSK 0430, ISO 105-C06, AATCC 61'),(32,'Sublimation Color Fastness Tester','Fastness','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/002_02.jpg','High quality temperature sensor inside heating plate.\n Individual heating control for each top and bottom plate.\n Easy to operate timer, temperature setting and convenient.\n Automatic heating stop and alarm.\n Standards : KSK 0651, ISO 105-P01, AATCC 117'),(33,'Rubbing Color Fastness Tester','Fastness','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/002_03.jpg','Motor-driven digital counter.\n Back and forth motion in a straight line.\n Sandpaper steel holder for specimen shifting prevention.\n Equipped with hard solid acrylic finger.\n Standards : KSK 0650, ISO 105-X12, AATCC 8'),(34,'Perspiration Fastness Tester','Fastness','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/002_04.jpg','Consists of stainless steel and acrylic material.\n Applies to all kinds of textile fabrics on color fastness to perspiration.\n Keeps the loading pressure with spring pressure rack during specimen drying.\n Standards : KSK 0715, ISO 105-E01/02/03/04, AATCC 15'),(35,'Fabric Water-Spray Tester','Fastness','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/002_05.jpg','Consists of stainless steel material exclusive of a funnel.\n Easy to remove the specimen.\n Consistent water flow by the precise spray nozzle.\n Standards : KSK 0590, ISO4920, AATCC22'),(36,'Yarn Length Tester','Fastness','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/002_06.jpg','Automatic stop of test by digital preset counter.\n Easy to remove the hank of yarn from reels by bend mechanism after winding and convenient operation. \n Equipped with speed controller.\n Soft start and braking by motor controller.'),(37,'Light Viewing Box','Fastness','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/002_07.jpg','Detect color difference(Metamerism) easily under 6 kinds of illumination. \n Designed according to ASTM D1729 and international standards.\n Application CIE standard illumination.\n Display using light sources on the screen.'),(38,'Computerized Dyestuff Storage Weighing Management System','Automation','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/004_01.jpg','Storage part consist of 64ea, 88ea, 112ea for standard. \n You can add easily storage part with customized rack system. \n Using servo controller speed up X, Y, Z robot.\n It takes a minute and half to measure 4 combinations. (Standard for 64ea) \n Weighing range : 0.01g ~ 40kgs.\n Easy operation. (PC touch screen)\n More specific control by servo motor.(262144P/Rev 18bit, ABS encoder) \n Easy of the maintenance\n Wherever you can find the part of control system and motor (JAPAN brand) easily.\n Using special bearing made in GERMAN is against dust, impact.\n Possible to check the data of Dyekeep System in ERP program.\n Easy to input the details of dyestuff with bar code scanner.\n Minimize the redyeing - automatic searching target dyestuff.\n Checking of consumption dyestuff - daily, monthly, annual.\n Korean, English, Chinese program.'),(39,'Computerized Dyestuff Weighing Management System','Automation','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/004_02.jpg','Data(Recipe) interface with color office by ERP or barcode system. \n Two precise balance, large & small. (Weighing range : 0.01g ~ 40kg)\n Easy operation with wide touch screen. (15 inch PC touch)\n Prevent redyeing with print out the result of weighing.\n Individual dyestuff lot management. (Optional : Barcode printer & scanner) \n Price calculation per recipe.\n Checking of consumption dyestuff. (Daily, Monthly, Annual)\n Moving controller which user can control any direction. (Left & right - 180) \n Korean, English, Chinese program.'),(40,'Dyestuff Dissolving Transfer System','Automation','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/04_01.jpg','Dyeing Schedule is transmitted to DCPM and work is in progress by dyeing machines,and by checking the status, \nit manages production work in real time\nDyestuff input amount and status on each dyeing machine are consisted synthetically through On-Line Interface and\ncomputer for dyestuff receipts and disbursements.\nERP, DCPM, TCS, etc. are integrated and it enables its dyeing operation of standardized method.'),(41,'Auxiliary Weighing Transfer System','Automation','http://www.daelimlab.com/home_en/images/product/04_02.jpg','Dyeing Schedule is transmitted to DCPM and work is in progress by dyeing machines and by checking the status,\n   it manages production work in real time.\n Aux. input amount and status on each machine are consisted synthetically through On-Line Interface and computer for aux.\n   receipts and disbursements.\n ERP, DCPM, TCS, etc. are integrated and it enables its dyeing operation of standardized method.');
